with Temp_Folder_With_Lambda_File('file_in_layer') as temp_folder:
    params = {'layer_name': 'layer_created_via_s3', 'description':
        'this is a test layer', 'runtimes': ['python3.8']}
    lambda_layer = Lambda_Layer(**params)
    result = lambda_layer.create_from_folder_via_s3(temp_folder.folder)
    self.assert_lambda_created_ok(params, result)
